'''Hugo Borchardt''' ([[Juniu 6]], [[1844]]-[[Mayu 8]], [[1924]]) metung yang talaimbentu kareng armas ampong metung yang, mibait king [[Magdeburg]], [[Germany]].  Bantug ya kareng kayang inimbentung [[Borchardt C-93]] pistol ampo ing [[Sharps-Borchardt Model 1878]] ripli (rifle).

Inyang [[1860]]  minta ya king [[United States]], at inyang [[1872]] meging yang Superintendent ning Obra para keng [[Pioneer Breech-Loading Arms Co.]] (Trenton, Mass.).  Inyang [[1874]] meging yang foreman para keng [[Singer Corporation|Singer Sewing Machine Co.]], kaibat meging ya empleadu keng [[Colt's Manufacturing Company|Colt's Patent Firearms Manufacturing Co.]], kaibat minta ya king [[Winchester Repeating Arms Company|Winchester Repeating Arms Co.]], kaibat meging yang Superintendent keng  [[Sharps Rifle Co.]] inyang  [[Juniu 1]], [[1876]].


